<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Bootstrap Example</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

{{> nav.hbs}}

<div class="tab-content">
    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade in active" id="home">
        <div class="container">

            <h1>Gracias por querer adoptar una mascota :) </h1>
            <h3>Estos datos seran publicados en nuestro foro para agilizar el proceso de adopcion </h3>
            <br>
            <form>
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <label for="nombre">Nombre</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="nombre">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <label for="apellido">Apellido</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="apellido">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control is-invalid" id="inputEmail4"
                           placeholder="Email" required>
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">
                        Por favor ingresa el email donde te llegará las sugerencias de mascotas y desde aqui tambien
                        podras cancelar tu publicacion de adpcion
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">¿Que mascota te gustaria adoptar?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">Perro</option>
                            <option value="2">Gato</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">¿Que tamaño de mascota aproximado preferis?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">Perro</option>
                            <option value="2">Gato</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">¿Que sexo de mascota preferis?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">Macho</option>
                            <option value="2">Hembra</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">¿Que edad aproximada que preferis?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">0-3</option>
                            <option value="2">4-6</option>
                            <option value="2">7-9</option>
                            <option value="2">Mayor a 9</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">¿Ya tenes mascotas?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">SI</option>
                            <option value="2">NO</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">Si ya tenes mascotas... ¿Cuantas tenes?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">0</option>
                            <option value="2">1</option>
                            <option value="2">2</option>
                            <option value="2">Mayor a 3</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="inputEmail4">¿Tenes patio en tu casa?</label>
                    <div>
                        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                            <option selected>Seleccioná</option>
                            <option value="1">SI</option>
                            <option value="2">NO</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <br>
                <br>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Publicar</button>
                <br>
                <br>
                <br>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="registroMascota">

    </div>
    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="references">ccc</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>